"{\"uid\": \"eonline.com-news-1405105-we-tried-the-2024-olympics-anti-sex-bed-the-results-may-shock-you\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"At the 2024 Olympics, the \\\"anti-sex\\\" beds from the 2020 Tokyo Games are making a return-but here's the hard truth about them.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone Bilesisn't the only Olympic iconmaking a comebackat the2024 Paris Summer Games.\", \"from\": 127, \"to\": 213, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After all, she-along with the thousands of athletes from across the globe-will be sleeping on anAirweavebed, whichwent viral during the 2020 Tokyo Olympicsfor its fragile appearance andso-called \\\"anti-sex\\\" appeal.\", \"from\": 215, \"to\": 428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the COO of the Japanese companyBrett Thorntonbelieves the disreputable label is a \\\"blessing in disguise.\\\"\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The funny part is, there was no truth to that,\\\" he exclusively told E!\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"News, explaining thatCOVID-19 protocols at the timewere what inhibited athletes from mingling in the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 714, \"end\": 729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999608917, \"rank\": 3.9267633822913874e-11, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The rumor was that the Olympic teams did not want athletes sleeping together, so they designed this flimsy cardboard bed so people would not do that.\\\"\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But these beds-whichincludes a cardboard frameand a mattress consisting of AirFiber-are actually a game-changer, according to Thornton.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1010, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\", \"score\": 0.9980339719548865, \"rank\": 0.0007841291720621071, \"text\": \"Thornton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And how do they feelcompared to a traditional spring mattress or memory foam bed?\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I tested it out-and the results were quite surprising.\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"First of all, I have to admit that the beds dolookflimsy.\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1216, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even Thornton agreed, telling me when I recently went to check one out in-person, \\\"If you look from the side of the cardboard, people see it and are like, 'How could that be sturdy?'\\\"\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1222, \"end\": 1230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\", \"score\": 0.9980339719548865, \"rank\": 0.0007841291720621071, \"text\": \"Thornton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But looks can be deceiving.\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As I laid down on the bed, its frame did not budge or slip out of place.\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, it did not creak like other rickety furniture.\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The mattress-which is actually comprised of a padded slipcover and three individual cushions, each with a side of moderate firmness and another ranging from soft to extra firm-had asturdy bounce to it.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And while I did appreciate that the cushions in the mattress can be easily flipped and arranged to different configurations of varying firmness to support my shoulder, waist and legs, I found the softest option was still firmer than my memory foam bed.\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 2015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, as Thornton noted, an Airweave mattress is not made to be so plush that you can sink into it.\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2029, \"end\": 2037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\", \"score\": 0.9980339719548865, \"rank\": 0.0007841291720621071, \"text\": \"Thornton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But rather, it's a luxury firm bed that aims to align your spine depending on your body shape and to provide you with a longer, deeper sleep.\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2261, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you are sleeping at night and you are in memory foam and it's time to turn,\\\" he explained, \\\"you actually have to put so much effort to turn that you wake up from a deep sleep.\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You come out of deep REM and then it takes you another five minutes to get back in.\\\"\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Moreover, the large air pockets between the mattress' plastic fibers-and not to mention, the two giant air chambers on its cardboard bed frame-help drop the body's temperature for a cooler sleep, Thornton said.\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2727, \"end\": 2735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\", \"score\": 0.9980339719548865, \"rank\": 0.0007841291720621071, \"text\": \"Thornton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Your body core temp needs to drop about two degrees to fall asleep,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2826, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With AirFiber, you get there faster.\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 2864, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, athletes are falling asleep faster, which is gonna give you more energy the next day.\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because it's temperature regulatory, you are going to stay asleep longer.\\\"\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 3029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And when it's time topack up the Olympic Village for good, Thornton said the mattress' AirFiber cores-which can actually be cleaned by just spraying water onto it-can be recycled at a local processing plant as well.\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3064, \"end\": 3079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999608917, \"rank\": 3.9267633822913874e-11, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 3090, \"end\": 3098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\", \"score\": 0.9980339719548865, \"rank\": 0.0007841291720621071, \"text\": \"Thornton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is the only innovation in this industry,\\\" he told me.\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3308, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is the first time there is been actually something totally different or unique.\\\"\", \"from\": 3309, \"to\": 3395, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As for my verdict?\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite its viral nickname, there is actually nothing discouraging people from having sex on this bed.\", \"from\": 3416, \"to\": 3518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the end of the night, it all comes down to whether or not you want a plushier or firmer sleepover experience.\", \"from\": 3519, \"to\": 3631, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your source for entertainment news, celebrities, celeb news, and \\u200bcelebrity gossip.\", \"from\": 3633, \"to\": 3716, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Check out the hottest fashion, photos, movies and TV shows!\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a92025E!\", \"from\": 3778, \"to\": 3785, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Entertainment Television, LLC A Versant Media Company.\", \"from\": 3786, \"to\": 3840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3812, \"end\": 3815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"score\": 0.9788496841358151, \"rank\": 0.021607317373063272, \"text\": \"LLC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\"}, {\"begin\": 3818, \"end\": 3825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versant\", \"score\": 0.9999998811808908, \"rank\": 1.0004845633505568e-07, \"text\": \"Versant\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 3841, \"to\": 3861, \"entities\": []}]}"